high_descs: Turn to the left and walk past the counter, then turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the potato on the sink.
Step to the right to face the right side of the sink.
Put the potato in the right side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Cut the potato into slices in the right side of the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink with the potato slices.
Pick up a slice of potato in the right side of the sink.
Step to the left and face the microwave above the stove.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave, then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Place the potato slice on the edge of the kitchen table by a bottle of wine.
anns.task_desc: TO heat a slice of potato and place it on the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn around, take a step forward, turn right, go forward, turn right after passing the island, go forward to the sink drying rack.
Take the potato from the rack.
Move a step to the right.
Put the potato in the sink basin.
Take the small knife from the drying rack.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Put the knife in the sink basin.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn left, go forward, turn right to face the oven.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave above the oven. Take the potato slice from the oven.
Turn right, go straight to the counter, turn right, go forward past the counter, turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the chair, turn right to face the table.
Put the potato to the left of the closest bottle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on a table.

high_descs: Turn left before going around a counter that is on the right turning to the right passed the counter and move towards the sink
Grab potato from beside the sink and on the left side of the butter knife
Move slightly right towards the other side of the sink
Place the potato in the sink
Pick up the butter knife from the left side of the sink
Cut the potato into slices
Place the butter knife into the sink to the left of the potato
Pick up a slice of potato
Turn left towards the stove next to the sink
Open microwave and place potato slice in the microwave then close the microwave door before opening it after the slice has cooked and removing it from the microwave
Turn right and move towards the counter before going around the counter keeping it to the left before turning right and moving towards the table
Place the cooked slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Placing a cooked slice of potato on a table
